      "ja": "雨が降っています。傘を持っていません。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "zh": "別擔心。",
      "ja": "心配しないで。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you have an umbrella?",
      "zh": "你有傘嗎？",
      "ja": "傘を持っていますか？",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes I do.",
      "zh": "有的。",
      "ja": "はい、持っています。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What color is it?",
      "zh": "它是什麼顏色？",
      "ja": "何色ですか？",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's green and white.",
      "zh": "它是綠色和白色的。",
      "ja": "緑と白です。",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's big.",
      "zh": "它很大。",
      "ja": "大きいです。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow. It's really big.",
      "zh": "哇。它真的很大。",
