      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What time is it, Dad?",
      "zh": "爸爸，現在幾點？",
      "ja": "パパ、今何時ですか？",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's seven o'clock.",
      "zh": "七點鐘。",
      "ja": "7時です。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
