      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a lion.",
      "zh": "那是一隻獅子。",
      "ja": "ライオンです。",
      "time": "00:07:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm wiki.",
      "zh": "我是Wiki。",
      "ja": "私はウィキです。",
      "time": "00:07:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look at the pretty doll.",
      "zh": "看那漂亮的娃娃。",
      "ja": "きれいな人形を見て。",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want it.",
      "zh": "我想要它。",
      "ja": "欲しいです。",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "May I help you?",
      "zh": "我可以幫你嗎？",
      "ja": "お手伝いしましょうか？",
      "time": "00:07:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, please.",
      "zh": "是的，請幫忙。",
      "ja": "はい、お願いします。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How much is it?",
      "zh": "這多少錢？",
      "ja": "いくらですか？",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Five hundred one.",
      "zh": "五百零一。",
      "ja": "501です。",
      "time": "00:07:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's five hundred one.",
      "zh": "這是五百零一。",
      "ja": "501をどうぞ。",
      "time": "00:07:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like this car.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這輛車。",
      "ja": "この車が好きです。",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's two hundred one.",
      "zh": "它是兩百零一。",
      "ja": "201です。",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want this kind.",
      "zh": "我想要這種。",
      "ja": "これが欲しいです。",
      "time": "00:08:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's very nice.",
      "zh": "它非常好。",
      "ja": "とてもいいです。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:08:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "May I help you?",
      "zh": "我可以幫你嗎？",
      "ja": "お手伝いしましょうか？",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How much is it?",
      "zh": "這多少錢？",
      "ja": "いくらですか？",
      "time": "00:08:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's five dollars.",
      "zh": "五美元。",
      "ja": "5ドルです。",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want this hat.",
      "zh": "我想要這頂帽子。",
      "ja": "この帽子が欲しいです。",
      "time": "00:08:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How much is it?",
      "zh": "這多少錢？",
      "ja": "いくらですか？",
      "time": "00:08:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's ten dollars.",
      "zh": "十美元。",
      "ja": "10ドルです。",
      "time": "00:08:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sally, you look very pretty.",
      "zh": "莎莉，你看起來很漂亮。",
      "ja": "サリー、とてもきれいだね。",
      "time": "00:08:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Dad.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，爸爸。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、パパ。",
      "time": "00:08:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now, let's have lunch.",
      "zh": "現在，我們吃午餐吧。",
      "ja": "さあ、昼食にしましょう。",
      "time": "00:08:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look.",
      "zh": "看。",
      "ja": "見て。",
      "time": "00:08:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They do take one dough.",
      "zh": "他們確實拿了一個麵團。",
