      "time": "00:08:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:08:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who is he?",
      "zh": "他是誰？",
      "ja": "彼は誰ですか？",
      "time": "00:08:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He is my take one dough teacher.",
      "zh": "他是我的麵團老師。",
      "ja": "彼は私の生地の先生です。",
      "time": "00:08:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who is she?",
      "zh": "她是誰？",
      "ja": "彼女は誰ですか？",
      "time": "00:08:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She is my friend.",
      "zh": "她是我的朋友。",
      "ja": "彼女は私の友達です。",
      "time": "00:09:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She is wonderful.",
      "zh": "她很棒。",
      "ja": "彼女は素晴らしいです。",
      "time": "00:09:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:09:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who is she?",
      "zh": "她是誰？",
      "ja": "彼女は誰ですか？",
      "time": "00:09:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "zh": "我不知道。",
      "ja": "知りません。",
      "time": "00:09:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mike.",
      "zh": "麥克。",
      "ja": "マイク。",
      "time": "00:09:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is she your mom?",
      "zh": "她是你媽媽嗎？",
      "ja": "彼女はあなたのお母さんですか？",
      "time": "00:09:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, she's my mom.",
      "zh": "是的，她是我媽媽。",
      "ja": "はい、彼女は私の母です。",
      "time": "00:09:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's sing a song together.",
      "zh": "我們一起唱歌吧。",
      "ja": "一緒に歌いましょう。",
      "time": "00:09:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:09:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can't sing.",
      "zh": "我不會唱歌。",
      "ja": "歌えません。",
      "time": "00:09:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "La la la la.",
      "zh": "啦啦啦啦。",
      "ja": "ララララ。",
      "time": "00:09:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What time do you get up?",
      "zh": "你幾點起床？",
      "ja": "何時に起きますか？",
      "time": "00:09:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I get up at six.",
      "zh": "我六點起床。",
      "ja": "6時に起きます。",
      "time": "00:10:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I go to school at seven thirty.",
      "zh": "我七點半去學校。",
      "ja": "7時半に学校に行きます。",
      "time": "00:10:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:10:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're an early bird.",
      "zh": "你是早起的人。",
      "ja": "あなたは早起きですね。",
      "time": "00:10:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:10:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look.",
      "zh": "看。",
      "ja": "見て。",
      "time": "00:10:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a new bike.",
      "zh": "這是一輛新自行車。",
      "ja": "新しい自転車です。",
      "time": "00:10:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What a nice bike.",
      "zh": "多麼漂亮的自行車。",
      "ja": "なんて素敵な自転車。",
      "time": "00:10:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:10:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's very nice.",
      "zh": "它非常好。",
      "ja": "とてもいいです。",
      "time": "00:10:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who's bike is this?",
      "zh": "這是誰的自行車？",
      "ja": "これは誰の自転車ですか？",
      "time": "00:10:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's Mike's.",
      "zh": "是麥克的。",
      "ja": "マイクのです。",
      "time": "00:10:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mike, is this your bike?",
      "zh": "麥克，這是你的自行車嗎？",
      "ja": "マイク、これはあなたの自転車ですか？",
      "time": "00:10:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:10:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's mine.",
      "zh": "是我的。",
      "ja": "私のです。",
      "time": "00:10:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:10:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You have a nice bike.",
      "zh": "你有一輛漂亮的自行車。",
      "ja": "いい自転車を持っていますね。",
      "time": "00:10:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:10:41"
    }
  ]
